msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"Hey, Makoto! As long as we're talking, let's REALLY\n"
"talk, whaddya say!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Huh? Oh, sure, that's fine..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid "Excellent!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"Then let's get down to brass tacks and find out where\n"
"we stand on all the big issues!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"So, what should we discuss? Politics? The economy?\n"
"International affairs!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid "Wait, hold on. Instead of a big, serious discussion..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"...can't we just have a normal conversation? That's\n"
"the best way to learn about people, I think."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid "What do you mean by a \"normal conversation\"?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid "Umm... Well, for example..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid "What do you like to do in your spare time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"Study, of course! I'm a student, aren't I? A student\n"
"must be a studying professional!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"And of course my duties as the chairperson of the\n"
"morals committee keep me quite busy, as well!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"It's my duty to foster an environment in which we can\n"
"all focus on our studies!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "Okay, but...what else?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"Like when you're at home, or you just have some time\n"
"to kill?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid "If I have time to kill, I study!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid "I...see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"Hahaha! This is fun! Okay, my turn. Makoto! What do\n"
"you like to do in your spare time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"Um, you know, just normal stuff. Watch TV, play video\n"
"games..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid "Huh? And this helps you study...how?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"N-No, it's not about studying. It's just for fun, ya\n"
"know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"But doing things \"just for fun\" serves no purpose!\n"
"There must be more to it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid ""
"You wouldn't spend your valuable time doing something\n"
"useless, would you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0024"
msgid "Relating to your friends"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid "Seriously, just for fun"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid ""
"Sorry, that's all there is to it. It's just something\n"
"fun to do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"Impossible! There must be a reason, you just haven't\n"
"realized it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"Which means this is a perfect opportunity for you to\n"
"reflect and learn something about yourself!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Crap...if I don't come up with an answer that makes\n"
"him happy, we'll never get anywhere...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid "Actually, it IS studying"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid ""
"Sometimes, it pretty much IS studying. Like some games\n"
"have to do with history and stuff..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid "Unacceptable!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"Things like that are more likely to twist the truth\n"
"than teach you anything useful!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid ""
"If you want to learn about the past, crack open a\n"
"history book!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid "O-Okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I could keep arguing about this, but...it's probably\n"
"better if I don't.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0037"
msgid "So? Can you think of any other reasons?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0038"
msgid "What's wrong? Why have you fallen silent?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid "Just give me one good reason. Come on, out with it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>He can insist all he wants, but in the end...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0041"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But...maybe there *is* a good reason. Like getting\n"
"into something, and talking to people about it...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>So maybe...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"You know how it's useful? It helps give you something\n"
"to talk about with other people!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0044"
msgid "Something to talk about...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"Like when you see something awesome on TV, or some\n"
"awesome game, and you want to share it with someone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0046"
msgid ""
"You find other people who feel the same way, and\n"
"that's how you make friends. See?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid "Wh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0048"
msgid "Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh—!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid "I once was blind, but now I see!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0050"
msgid "Wh-What the heck!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid "That kind of thing has plagued me for years..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid ""
"I've tried making friends, but whenever I would make\n"
"conversation, it would die after a few minutes..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid "And now...I've finally found the answer..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0054"
msgid "I need to study more games! More TV shows!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid "N-No, you don't need to \"study\" them..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"Ahh, I'm so ashamed of myself! If there was a hole\n"
"somewhere around here, I'd totally go hide in it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"I let it get to me, I wasted all that time... I never\n"
"saw the blind spot in my studies!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0058"
msgid ""
"I'm a complete embarrassment! I'm not qualified to\n"
"even be on the morals committee, let alone lead it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid "I-I don't think it's really that big of a deal..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0060"
msgid "Thank you, Professor Makoto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0061"
msgid "Professor!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0062"
msgid ""
"You've taught me a most valuable lesson! You've earned\n"
"my respect, and the title of professor!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0063"
msgid "Th-That's gonna make things super awkward...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0064"
msgid "Hahaha! There's no need to be modest, Professor!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0065"
msgid ""
"I can't wait for your next lesson! And until then, I\n"
"will strive to learn as much as I can on my own!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0066"
msgid "Well then, Professor—by your leave!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0067"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Without waiting for a reply, Taka ran off.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0068"
msgid "Professor..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0069"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Although, thinking about it...I didn't totally hate\n"
"it.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0070"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Professor Makoto...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0071"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Taka's <CLT><CLT 3>Report Card<CLT><CLT 23> has been updated based on your\n"
"experience with him.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0072"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>You just unlocked the skill <CLT><CLT 3>Attentive Influence<CLT><CLT 23>!\n"
"Give yourself a pat on the back. You've earned it!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0073"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>After we were done, I decided to head back to my room\n"
"for a while...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
